Definition: a fundamentalist Islamic revivalist movement generally characterized by moral conservatism and the literal interpretation of the Koran and the attempt to implement Islamic values in all aspects of life
Synonyms: noun, person, islamist, religious_movement, a, fundamentalist, Islamic, revivalist, movement, generally, characterized, by, moral, conservatism, and, the, literal, interpretation, of, Koran, attempt, to, implement, values, in, all, aspects, life
Category: noun.group
